          "instruction": "Answer the questions based on the audio.",
          "prompt_html": "<h1>MATCHING INFORMATION TO CATEGORIES 24</h1><p><strong>Questions 15 - 20</strong></p><p><strong>Choose the correct type of pie for each statement.</strong></p><p>Question 15 These pies often contained seafood.</p><ul><li><p>A - Ancient Roman pies</p></li><li><p>B - Animated pies</p></li><li><p>C - Coffyns</p></li><li><p>D - Mince pies</p></li><li><p>E - True pies</p></li></ul><p>Question  16 These pies used solid fat instead of oil.</p><ul><li><p>A - Ancient Roman pies</p></li><li><p>B - Animated pies</p></li><li><p>C - Coffyns</p></li><li><p>D - Mince pies</p></li><li><p>E - True pies</p></li></ul><p>Question 17 These pies feature in a well-known children's rhyme.</p><ul><li><p>A - Ancient Roman pies</p></li><li><p>B - Animated pies</p></li><li><p>C - Coffyns</p></li><li><p>D - Mince pies</p></li><li><p>E - True pies</p></li></ul><p>Question 18 These pies contained live animals or people.</p><ul><li><p>A - Ancient Roman pies</p></li><li><p>B - Animated pies</p></li><li><p>C - Coffyns</p></li><li><p>D - Mince pies</p></li><li><p>E - True pies</p></li></ul><p>Question 19 These pies had inedible pastry.</p><ul><li><p>A - Ancient Roman pies</p></li><li><p>B - Animated pies</p></li><li><p>C - Coffyns</p></li><li><p>D - Mince pies</p></li><li><p>E - True pies</p></li></ul><p>Question 20 These pies were banned for a period of time.</p><ul><li><p>A - Ancient Roman pies</p></li><li><p>B - Animated pies</p></li><li><p>C - Coffyns</p></li><li><p>D - Mince pies</p></li><li><p>E - True pies</p></li></ul>",
